- There are at least 11,778 GLSL repos on <a href="https://github.com/search?q=language:GLSL">GitHub</a>
- GLSL first developed in <a href="../lists/originCommunities.html#openGlArchitectureReviewBoard">OpenGL Architecture Review Board</a>
- file extensions for GLSL include glsl, fp, frag, frg, fs, fsh, fshader, geo, geom, glslf, glslv, gs, gshader, rchit, rmiss, shader, tesc, these, vert, vrx, vsh and vshader
- The  Google BigQuery Public Dataset GitHub snapshot shows 12k users using GLSL in 14k repos on <a href="https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=language:GLSL">GitHub</a>
- Explore GLSL snippets on <a href="http://www.rosettacode.org/wiki/Category:GLSL">Rosetta Code</a>
- GLSL appears in the <a href="https://www.tiobe.com/tiobe-index/">TIOBE Index</a>
- GLSL <a href="language-server-protocol.html">LSP</a> <a href="https://github.com/svenstaro/glsl-language-server">implementation</a>
- <a href="pygments.html">Pygments</a> supports <a href="https://github.com/pygments/pygments/blob/master/pygments/lexers/graphics.py">syntax highlighting</a> for GLSL
